    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个医疗科技场景下的流程图，核心是从LabAnalyzer开始，经过HIPAA安全保险库来处理患者数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是LabAnalyzer，然后进入HIPAA_Vault这个判断节点？我想确认一下Vault在这里是作为决策点还是单纯的数据存储？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Vault既是安全存储也是关键决策点。数据从LabAnalyzer流入Vault后，会流向PatientRecords，然后有一个分支判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那PatientRecords之后分Yes/No两条路径：Yes回到HIPAA_Vault，No则流向一个叫OtherFamilyChance的节点。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "OtherFamilyChance"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，OtherFamilyChance代表其他家庭有机会响应的情况。不过PatientRecords之后的Yes分支，我想调整一下——不是回到Vault，而是进入一个叫RoundStart的子图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RoundStart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我创建RoundStart子图，把Yes分支指向子图内的D节点，也就是HIPAA_Vault。然后D再连接到CheckResponse判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RoundStart",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "CheckResponse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CheckResponse也有Yes/No分支。Yes走向CompareAnswer，由DiagnosticEngine处理；No的话直接到OtherFamilyChance。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckResponse",
        "CompareAnswer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
