      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CompareAnswer本身也是一个判断节点吗？我看到它后面还有Yes/No分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CompareAnswer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，CompareAnswer比较答案后，Yes表示FamilyContinues，家庭可以继续，由DiagnosticEngine处理；No则退回OtherFamilyChance。",
